text: Aleksandra Ristovska (; born 21 August 1995) is a Macedonian footballer who plays as a forward for 1. liga club ŽFK Tiverija Istatov and the North Macedonia women's national team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Macedonian women's footballers Category:North Macedonia women's international footballers
